name: Injustice Judge & Court of Disgrace
description:
"Injustice Judge & Court of Disgrace"
Sins of Greed

1750 x 2304 px
MP4
12 Seconds


I save you even if you rascal if you got money, on this court of disgrace only the rich who will win the case who will win this world...

I will never hand the freedom to the kind of you who got nothing...

This is the art in which I try to depict the tyranny and irony of the world the unjust the untrue in this world...
People who live on higher sometimes forget about the other struggle...

I hate the kind of people who exploit other people that try to make fortune from them. they are one of the worst people...
